# Project-Specific Ignores
# ========================================

# CodeMonkey Toolkit (third-party asset pack helpers)
# Both variations to catch any naming differences
[Aa]ssets/CodeMonkey/
[Aa]ssets/Codemonkey/
Codemonkey/
CodeMonkey/

# ========================================
# Optional - Uncomment if needed
# ========================================

# Recovery/Backup Folders
# [Aa]ssets/_Recovery/

# Test Scenes
# [Aa]ssets/Scenes/Test*.unity

# Documentation Drafts
# *_DRAFT.md

# ========================================
# Notes
# ========================================

# Asset meta data should only be ignored when the corresponding asset is also ignored
# This is handled by Unity automatically - meta files for tracked assets will remain

# If you have additional third-party assets to exclude, add them below:
# [Aa]ssets/ThirdPartyAssetName/

